age/1?post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n而帝吧班周圍攪事的支那人已經比人起底係低收入人士, 銀行連一萬人仔都無<br />\n邊會捨得次次做五毛都係黑市買新ac用一次就唔要,呢班人連買份排骨蒸都有困難"},{"pid":"202c3ef8dde5f8658509caa2f95b91c727f4881b","tid":1577803,"uid":36592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T02:33:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75ce2339371a73d2b25555707cc361b857e4f75d","tid":1577803,"uid":144492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T02:36:47.000Z","msg":"等緊林7偉寄信屌美國國會"},{"pid":"f2d05ea470ea1444d3c6cf62fe452ef687ea0ade","tid":1577803,"uid":261332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0ffa2fb285a484683c101dde1d992d7f6d764560","tid":1577803,"uid":36592,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T01:22:03.000Z","msg":"大專學界國際事務代表團做左咁多野FB, Twitter竟然咁少關注？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HKHIIAD/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHKHIIAD%2F&d=RXc9xvVhXBFlPE4DV6Zf5Hfp3ZHOIdf2SFoQnphXrww%3D&h=b5cdd5b5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HKHIIAD/</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hkhiiad\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhkhiiad&d=RXc9xvVhXBFlPE4DV6Zf5Hfp3ZHOIdf2SFoQnphXrww%3D&h=ec60442a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/hkhiiad</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T02:37:19.000Z","msg":"老老實實，唔一定要所有做實事既都需要大肆宣揚架。<br />\n有好多時fly under the radar 係比受注目重要。<br />\n<br />\n就好似太古廣場6 月幫示威者咁，根本人地係想低調幫，唔想你地不停感激又盛咁。而家就搞到人地做左箭靶。"},{"pid":"492540ef66e01ca888b70cf23145f510dfd7e5d2","tid":1577803,"uid":10812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T02:42:05.000Z","msg":"唔係柒呀<br />\n係好撚恐怖呀"}]}